		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#8d29b4" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#8d29b4">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="442" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">一段时间后<span color="#ffdfbf">(70s/首次40s)</span><span>或生命值低于</span><span color="#ffbfbf">70%</span><span>时，摹结株将枝节插入地面进行蓄力，获得暂时的</span><span textDecoration="underline">虚界护罩</span><span>，并持续在场地内召唤幽生蓟，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">10%</span><span>(</span><span color="#99ff99">10</span><span>级「</span><span textDecoration="underline">蚀破</span><span>」)；13s后蓄力完成，产生大爆炸，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">300%</span><span>(</span><span color="#99ff99">60</span><span>)伤害。<br/>击破护罩后，摹结株将瘫痪12s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">摹结株能够在13种首领之间变换，在不同的战斗中，存在3种摹结株变体，每组的变体都不同，会随机施放技能。<br/>摹结株仅仅起模仿作用，BOSS的原有独特机制会尽数丢失。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="610" y="159" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="564" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">摹结株有3种摹结株变体，对应下面三组；每次击败后都会刷新另外一组，每组的技能均控制在9个，且均有5个存在可附加蚀破的强化技能：</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
