				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">瘫痪</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="9" y="1169" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">开场</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="9" y="1091" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="57" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">瘫痪再恢</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="733" width="442" height="154" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「蚀破」：角色被附加「蚀破」时，将在1s后扣除前台角色一定的生命值。「蚀破」拥有不同的等级，<span color="#ffccbf">n</span><span>级「蚀破」扣除</span><span color="#ffccbf">(1%+50)*n</span><span>点生命值，若在间隔T内连续施加多种「蚀破」，则它们的等级会相加，并在脱离伤害的1s后结算蚀破总伤害。<br/></span></p>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">间隔 T<span fontFamily="宋体">∈</span><span color="#ffecbf">(0.1,1] </span><span>s<br/></span><span>虚界护罩：每次</span><span color="#ffffbf">元素攻击</span><span>可削减该护盾</span><span color="#ffccbf">1</span><span>点，</span><span color="#bfdfff">带有夜魂性质的攻击</span><span>则削减</span><span color="#ffccbf">3</span><span>点，没有冷却。这种护罩在被击破之前，敌人将免疫所有伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="610" y="1228" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="404" height="20" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">摹结株仅仅起模仿作用，原BOSS的特性或机制不会保留。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1220" width="496" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深渊抗性：正常 70%，瘫痪 0%，瘫痪再恢 35%，开场370%。若使其再次开盾，但未进行破盾，则抗性会恢复至<span color="#ff9999">[正常]</span><span>，而非</span><span color="#ff9999">[瘫痪再恢]</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="599" y="262" fontFamily="Sen" fontSize="60" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9999" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.4">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="Sen" fontSize="60" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9999">GROUP ONE </p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="599" y="582" fontFamily="Sen" fontSize="60" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9999" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.4">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="Sen" fontSize="60" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9999">GROUP TWO </p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="610" y="320" width="579" height="245" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="22" fontWeight="bold" lineHeight="144%" color="#ffffff">兆载<span fontStyle="italic">永劫龙兽</span><span fontStyle="italic" color="#ffebbf">A</span><span fontStyle="italic"> / 翠翎恐蕈</span><span fontStyle="italic" color="#99ff85">B</span><span fontStyle="italic"> / 树 (掣电</span><span fontStyle="italic" color="#ffacff">C</span><span fontStyle="italic"> 急冻</span><span fontStyle="italic" color="#99ffff">D</span><span fontStyle="italic"> 爆炎</span><span fontStyle="italic" color="#ff9999">E</span><span fontStyle="italic">)<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="8" color="#ff9999"><br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffebbf">A</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「巡空游辰」-命中与扫尾造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#b8b8b8">75%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；强化施加</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff99">15</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">级「蚀破」；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffebbf">A</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「垦土掘岩」-两次挖掘造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#b8b8b8">60%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害，扫尾造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#b8b8b8">75%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffebbf">A</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「散落洪流」-散弹造成对应元素</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#ffff99">100%,30%,10%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff85">B</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「暮羽归扇」-孢子造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff85">45%,22.5%,4.5%,0.45%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；强化施加</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff99">5</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">级「蚀破」；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff85">B</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「蕈王玷土」-前两段普攻均造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff85">60%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；强化施加</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff99">5</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">级「蚀破」；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff85">B</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「蕈王疾舞」-4段攻击均造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff85">120%,60%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#ffacff">C</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「紫雷迷林」-持续性落雷造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#ffacff">40%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ffff">D</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「炙寒滨风」-收伞造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ffff">100%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；强化施加</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff99">15</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">级「蚀破」；<br/></span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#ff9999">E</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">「铁花秽浪」-锤点和震波分别造成</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#ff9999">100%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">和</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#ff9999">50%</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">伤害；强化施加</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16" color="#99ff99">15</span><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W01" fontSize="16">级「蚀破」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="627" y="289" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="22" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9999" width="76" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
